  "3170840": {
    "name": "Election Tycoon: Trump vs Harris",
    "steam_appid": 3170840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Step into the intense world of U.S. politics with Election Tycoon! In this real-time strategy game, you'll take on the role of a presidential candidate in the 2024 elections. Whether you choose to be Donald Trump, Kamala Harris, or create your own independent candidate, your goal is to sway the nation and secure your place in the White House.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/299bc3e5b7f96127cfb04cfe4041b499.webp?t=1744400138\" width=473 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Success in Election Tycoon requires more than just promises. You'll need to strategically build fund, vote, and propaganda buildings across different states. Fund buildings help you raise the money needed to power your campaign, vote buildings increase your support in key states, and propaganda buildings shift political alignments in your favor. But be careful—every decision counts!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/d4ffd727607b207f6135b5b2935dacae.webp?t=1744400138\" width=473 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Each state in Election Tycoon is a battleground with its own dynamics. Choose from different map modes to analyze the situation and deploy your resources where they’ll have the most impact. Whether you're focusing on swing states or reinforcing your strongholds, the path to victory is in your hands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>While winning the election is the ultimate goal, there's an extra layer of satisfaction in turning the entire map to your party's color. It's a visual representation of your success and a fun challenge for those who want to leave their mark on the country's history.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/0cb21cb5d9168704ef1e15443bb4824f.webp?t=1744400138\" width=473 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Election Tycoon is designed to be accessible to all players, but true mastery will require careful planning and strategy. With multiple factors to consider and optimize, creating the perfect campaign will test even the most seasoned strategists.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Election Tycoon offers a variety of fun and challenging achievements that add an extra layer of flavor to the game. These achievements are designed to be both rewarding and entertaining, pushing you to explore different strategies and scenarios to unlock them all. Can you rise to the challenge and earn them all?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/72c1782be68adcf7ddf6db773a84e890.webp?t=1744400138\" width=262 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Play as Trump, Harris, or create your own candidate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Build and manage fund, propaganda, and vote buildings across the U.S.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Complete missions to upgrade and enhance your campaign.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Explore different map modes to assess state dynamics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Turn the entire map to your party’s color for a visual victory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Unlock unique, fun, and challenging achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170840/extras/657c79c00df13a85952d3419ea88d6f7.webp?t=1744400138\" width=17 height=16 /></span>Easy to learn but challenging to master, offering depth for strategy enthusiasts.<br><br><strong>Wishlist now!</strong><br>Wishlist to get updated when we release. Every wishlist helps our development of the game!",
